  "title": "ADMINISTRATIVE ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></p><p>Licensed Employment Agency is looking for a responsible and detail-oriented ADMINISTRATIVE ASSISTANT to join our team.</p><p>The successful candidate must be eligible to register as “Other EA Personnel” with MOM</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><p>- Handle work passes online application and issuance</p><p>- Prepare worker resumes using company templates</p><p>- Record, update, and maintain data, including e-filing and documentation</p><p>- Coordinate onboarding arrangements and bookings</p><p>- Support daily administrative tasks related to recruitment operations</p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><p><strong>- CEI certificate required</strong></p><p>- Able to register as Other EA Personnel with MOM</p><p>- Good organizational and documentation skills</p><p>- Careful, responsible, and able to handle confidential information</p><p><br />Mon-Fri: 9am - 6:30pm</p><p>Beside MacPherson MRT Station</p>",
